summary: AN ORDINANCE abandoning the unexpended and unencumbered balances in certain appropriations made from the General Fund, Park Fund, Library Fund, City-County Health Fund, Meat Inspection Fund, Special Nursing - Visiting Nurse Service, Emergency Fund, Cumulative Reserve Fund, Engineering Department Operating Fund, Public Health Revolving, Urban Renewal Operating Fund, Motor Transportation Fund, Employees' Retirement System, Building Department Operating Fund and Seattle Center Fund.
